CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1774461963
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to man who died
OL,4,Cafter disturbance at pub in seaside
OL,5,Ctown
OL,7,FOriginally from Hull, Mr Smith was
OL,8,Fliving in Halifax.
OL,10,FIn a tribute, his family said: "A
OL,11,Fdearly loved son, brother, fiance,
OL,12,Funcle, cousin and friend was taken
OL,13,Faway from us all in devastating
OL,14,Fcircumstances.
OL,16,F"He will continue to live on in our
OL,17,Fhearts and memories as the kind,
OL,18,Floving, generous, hardworking and
OL,19,Flarger than life character that he was.
OL,26,@sD@arr
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36903
